data.text:
Clone of SingStar for Mac

UltraStar Deluxe is an open source karaoke game for Mac with which you can sing and perform your favorite songs. It is very similar to the popular SingStar for video game consoles.

More than 10,000 songs available.

The fact that UltraStar Deluxe is an open source game means that your are free to modify its content according to your needs. Adjust UltraStar Deluxe and enjoy fun moments with your friends.

Features

Karaoke game for Mac.

Achieve the maximum score depending on your intonation and rhythm.

Obtain all kinds of additional material from the user community.

Party mode for up to 12 players.

Compatible with your PC's microphone, and even with SingStar microphones.

Get free songs for UltraStar Deluxe, tune your voice and enjoy yourself without leaving the house. If you're a potential artist, all you need to do is download UltraStar Deluxe free.

Requirements and additional information:

To download the songs prepared and offered by the software and Internet connection is required.
